Package: membervars
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Convert member variable naming conventions in source files
 membervars rewrites C/C++ identifiers to convert between m_<name> and
 <name>_ conventions while skipping comments and string literals.
